{"tid":295630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"董建華稱對香港未來感樂觀：最大原因係林鄭做特首","createTime":"2017-06-24T02:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T03:51:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c62c46bbbd0779b410a0d746d7555cc34e4394a6","tid":295630,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170624/large/1498269629_3eac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170624%2Flarge%2F1498269629_3eac.jpg&h=159c3db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n候任行政長官林鄭月娥將於7月1日正式就任，前行政長官、全國政協副主席董建華表示對香港未來感到樂觀，最大理由就是選出林鄭月娥為下任行政長官，認為她能帶領香港人前進。<br />\n<br />\n董建華出席電台節目時指，相信林鄭月娥是有智慧、有奉獻精神及有遠見的領導者，形容她能幹、勤奮，受香港人和中央信任，認為她有能力應對眾多挑戰。他又感謝行政長官梁振英過去5年工作，認為梁堅定維護一國兩制，在不同領域作出巨大努力。<br />\n<br />\n他指隨著國家經濟發展，香港的金融中心可做大一兩倍，如電影業可重新發展，屆時將給予年輕人大量就業機會。"},{"pid":"7242b7725c3ad0ec7017da00e85bc1aec5b50689","tid":295630,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56869662&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56869662%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170624&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g79U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=57582d25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56869662%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170624&h=f2bc57b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56869662&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170624</a>"},{"pid":"becd03d9eb51c1f9f69826f7fb2aec0230a9d4ad","tid":295630,"uid":19013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:30:24.000Z","msg":"呢個老屎忽仲咁多野講，邊個做特首都搞唔掂"}